我花了好几年时间研究了

21
00:01:04.793 --> 00:01:07.625
of terrorism prosecutions in  the United States,
美国的涉恐案卷，

22
00:01:07.625 --> 00:01:09.894
and I've come to  the conclusion that the FBI
我得出一个结论：联邦调查局

23
00:01:09.894 --> 00:01:13.734
is much better at creating terrorists than it is at catching terrorists.
更擅长培养恐怖分子，而不是逮捕他们。

24
00:01:14.903 --> 00:01:16.917
In the 14 years since 9/11,
“9·11”发生后的14年间，

25
00:01:16.917 --> 00:01:20.501
