计划在时代广场引爆汽车炸弹。

30
00:01:30.327 --> 00:01:31.942
In those same 14 years,
同样在这14年间，

31
00:01:31.942 --> 00:01:33.574
the Bureau, however, has bragged
联邦调查局却不停在吹嘘

32
00:01:33.574 --> 00:01:36.155
about how it's foiled dozens of terrorism plots.
他们挫败了数十起恐怖主义阴谋。

33
00:01:36.765 --> 00:01:41.003
In all, the FBI has arrested more than 175 people
联邦调查局通过激进、秘密的反恐骗局

34
00:01:41.003 --> 00:01:44.449
in aggressive, undercover  conterterrorism stings.
总共逮捕了超过175人。

35
00:01:44.449 --> 00:01:47.287
These operations, which are usually led by an informant,
这些行动，通常由联邦调查局的线人领导，

36
00:01:47.287 --> 00:01:49.113
provide the means and opportunity,
他们出谋划策，提供机会

37
00:01:49.113 --> 00:01:51.045
and sometimes even the idea,
甚至直接授意，

38
00:01:51.045 --> 00:01:53.901
